title: Gobber Ninja Full v1.5
description:
You can be the next Gobber Ninja Master! This physic puzzle is a high-flying, fast-paced game that everyone will enjoy! 

With an average rating of 4.5 stars out of 5 and positive reviews, Gobber Ninja has even been nominated in several categories at the Canadian Videogames Awards! What are you waiting for? Gobber Ninja is THE action game to play!

***** FEATURES *****

- Go through 80+ levels to become the next Ninja Master!
- Improve your reaction skills and increase your speed to complete the challenges!
- Defeat the flies and catch all the stars for a complete victory!
- Change colors to succeed the events!

Will you be strong enough to take the challenge?
